  A  number  of  welfare  schemes  are 

being implemented in Uttar Pradesh without any discrimination.  A law has been 

enacted  in  U.P.  by  which  land  of  the  farmers  cannot  be  auctioned.    There  are 

schemes  like  Kanya  Vidya  Dhan  Yojana,  Pension  for  Women.    Unemployment 

allowance is being given to the unemployed.  Empowerment of all should be done 

without any discrimination.    

 

